title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 14 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 14 2022
description:
Dr. Marty Makary joins Clay and Buck to preview his 9/11 Commission-style report on U.S. covid response. Winklevoss twins sing Don't Stop Believin' after they fired 10% of staff at crypto startup. Even Don Lemon is asking whether Joe Biden is up to the job. Mike Pompeo on Biden's upcoming trip to Saudi Arabia. Alex Berenson told us on this show a year ago that the covid vaccines weren't working. Ukraine war rages on.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
